    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "48f61bad-2e16-4b71-a1c6-72423c772a57",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Corsican Pt2: End of the Mondegreens",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ANCESTRAL_BULLDOG",
        "PublicId": "128624532648",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 8943b399-8e00-4a7b-ae79-41863722c45a).Image",
        "Description": "Following our elimination of Helen West and the Mondegreen assassins stalking her, an anonymous client has requested that we take care of the head of the Mondegreen Muffin Agency itself. Thanks to the carelessness of the assassins, we now know their leader is none other than Emma Carlisle, a greedy and vile murderer. Eliminate Carlisle, along with the lawyer and undertaker she conspired with to create the Mondegreen Muffin Agency. Let&apos;s hope this target isn&apos;t a hydra, 47. Good luck.",
